                "Transparent Cash Flows — The revenue recognition order ([[Waterfall|Waterfall structure. Revenue distribution priority: ① Senior principal and interest → ② Operating costs → ③ Subordinated principal and interest → ④ Dividends → ⑤ Residual profit distribution. Distributed like water flowing from top to bottom.]]) must be stated explicitly in contracts and managed through an independent escrow account.",
