              "text": "Layer 1 (SPC): Singapore Nusantara Development Ltd.\n- Purpose: PF borrowing and Indonesia development execution\n- Capital structure: Senior PF $18B + RCPS $7B\n- Reality: Legal entity overseeing the entire project\n\nLayer 2 (SPV — for ABS issuance): Nusantara Income Receivable SPV\n- Purpose: Purchases rare earth export proceeds receivables (Offtake contracts) from SPC\n- Issuance: Issues ABS tokens using these receivables as collateral (ADDX platform)\n- Effect: SPC obtains immediate cash; ABS investors directly receive rare earth revenues\n\nLayer 3 (SPV — for equity tokenization): Nusantara Equity Token SPV\n- Purpose: Tokenizes a portion of SPC equity for sale to small investors on ADDX\n- Issuance: STO form, minimum investment $50,000\n- Effect: Expands subordinated equity to distributed investor base\n\nResult: Three independent entities operating separately, maximizing global investor base."
