              "text": "In 2024, IASB strengthened SPV consolidation standards through IFRS 10 amendments. With stricter de facto control criteria, SPVs that previously received off-balance-sheet treatment are increasingly being consolidated into parent companies. Obtaining a Consolidation Opinion from Big4 (KPMG, PwC, etc.) in advance has become essential in financial design."
