          "content": "You are reading the final chapter of this book.\n\nFrom when you first opened this book to now, I hope the lens through which you see finance has changed.\n\nFinance is not a complex formula. It is a structure that connects time, risk, and trust between those who need money and those who have money to spare. The distance between those who understand that structure and those who don't is not simply a difference in knowledge — it is a difference in opportunity.",
